ing: 1 (5 ounce) can tuna, drained and flaked
des: "People never guess this dip recipe is made with tuna. The liquid smoke gives it a unique flavor! Serve it with crackers."
ins: In a medium bowl, mix the Italian-style salad dressing, sour cream, seasoning salt, onion, liquid smoke and tuna. Chill in the refrigerator approximately 1 hour before serving.
